hue - a posix shell script to control your philips hue lights

How to install
put the hue file into $PATH.

How to configure
read https://developers.meethue.com/develop/get-started-2/

example:
USER="foo"
IP="bar"

USER is the api key you made.
IP is the bridges ip, you can figure this out by going into your router or using nmap.
